I came for lunch and ended up in Italy. 🇮🇹✨

Tarantella in Chiswick surprised me — cozy, authentic, and absolutely delicious.

🍝 Pasta that melts in your mouth
🍕 Pizza with a cheese pull that stopped time
🍹 And the spritz? Dangerously good.

If you’re craving Italian, start here. You’ll thank me later.

✨ When life gets hectic, a body massage is my reset button.
I spent the day at @spamassageuk and honestly? It was everything I didn’t know I needed. Warm vibes, expert hands, and the kind of calm that stays with you all weekend.

10/10 for the experience… and yes, I’m now officially obsessed with their oils and cozy spa room.

You need this kind of self-care moment.
Book your visit at www.spaandmassage.co.uk
Use code HAZ20 for £20 off - thank me later!

latestPosts.caption:
From live photos to a little video 🎥🤝
.
The sensation in my body?
Restless, wild, jet-lagged... and already planning the next trip.
Travel is my vitamin. My therapy. My favorite kind of chaos.
One street leads to another, one city opens the door to the next.
A quick bite, a new mood, a moment of magic - and suddenly I’m dreaming of the next place, the next passport stamp, the next story.
Work trip? Holiday? Who can tell anymore - I just know I’m not made to sit still.
.
